reviewText:
really cool if you have 15 minutes to kill and the urge to test your knowledge.

Let me be straight. it's not the hardest quiz ever. If you, like me, devoured maps as a child then this will be nothing more than showing off.
else it can be a good way to learn a little about the world.

highly recommned
